      "review_summary": "The PR adds a `__openclaw.runtimeOnlyEvent` transcript marker and filters runtime-only continuation prompts plus their immediate assistant delivery reports out of memory session-corpus ingestion.\n\nPR surface: Source +86, Tests +106, Docs +1. Total +193 across 10 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level: current main can still export a runtime-only continuation prompt and the following assistant delivery report through `buildSessionEntry`; I did not run a live cron plus Dreaming sweep in this read-only review.",
